Mary Kathleen SULLIVAN, by W. T. Scarborough, Her Guardian ad Litem, Appellant, v. Joseph E. CURRY et al., etc., Appellees. No. 6267. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. Oct. 13, 1930. For opinion below see 40 F.(2d) 948.

Before RUDKIN and WILBUR, Circuit Judges, and NORCROSS, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellees, ordered appeal dismissed for failure of appellant to file record and docket cause.
